  "history": "The client works with children who have learning disabilities and reports being pampered by parents with minimal consequences during childhood. There is a pattern of ongoing conflicts with authority figures. The client appears unaccustomed to handling rejection or criticism, which may stem from their upbringing. This background likely contributes to current difficulties in managing negative feedback and assertively addressing disagreements with authority.",
